Already told you…

[quote=“Sick of Air, post:8, topic:127518”]Start > Control Panel > System > Advanced > Environmental Variables.

Classpath

C:\Program Files\Java\Java\jdk1.6.0_02\bin\

Path

c:\Windows\System32\;”C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_02\bin\;C:\Program Files\Common Files\Adobe\AGL

Those are what I use, and it works fine.[/quote]
